Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.56,Prologue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\t(0,1950,\c&HAA00AA)}com a aparência de uma criança, mas a mente de um adulto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:42.64,Prologue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\c&HAA00AA\t(0,1020,\c&H0000FF)}Seu nome é Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:46.98,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Cheio de contradições, o ônibus continua seguindo em frente
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:46.98,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Mujunmansaishita mama hashiri-tsuzukeru bus
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:53.44,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}E inocentemente sorrimos enquanto embarcamos nele
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:53.44,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Nokkatta boku-ra wa mujaki ni warau
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:58.36,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Existem placas em todos os lados em que olhamos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:58.36,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Migi-hidari nigiyaka na sign ga afurete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:04.41,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Podemos confiar em você se nos perdermos, motorista?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:04.41,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Mayottara mi o makasu desu yo ne, driver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:14.13,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Será que ainda haveriam crimes se não existisse mais maldade?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:14.13,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Waruginakutemo tsumi wa umaremasu ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.59,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Onde está a resposta? Alguém sabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.59,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Kotae wa doko ni kakusarete'ru no somebody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:26.81,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Não desista, pense um pouco mais! Questione! Responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:26.81,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Akiramenaide mō choi kangaete Question! Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:38.28,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Toque seu rosto enquanto estiver na escuridão
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:38.28,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\1a}Kurayami ni ukande'ru sono hoho ni fureru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:50.00,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}E agarre a justiça que ninguém pode abandonar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:50.00,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\1a}Daremo ga yuzurenai seigi o idaite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:55.67,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}A resposta sempre esteve aqui! Tudo mundo sabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:55.67,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Kotae wa koko ni chanto aru ja nai everybody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:01.55,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Mas mesmo com ela, eu sei que muitos corações ainda vão duvidar!\N — Questione! Responda!
